{"title":"Salsa Cycles Warbird Gets New Kits and Colors","link":"https://theradavist.com/salsa-cycles-warbird-2025-kits-and-colors/","date":1739376812000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_07.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_07.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_07.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_07.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em><a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/salsa-cycles/\" target=\"_blank\">Salsa Cycles</a>‘ gravel race bike, Warbird, is designed for endurance gravel road riding and racing, and for 2025, it kept the same chassis and geometry, but received new colors and build kits, let’s check it out…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_05.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_05.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_05.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_05.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_04.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_04.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_04.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_04.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_06.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_06.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_06.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_06.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Salsa Warbird Quick Hits</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Carbon frameset with geometry focused on stability and comfort</li>\n<li>Class 5 VRS™ soaks up vibrations on rough gravel roads</li>\n<li>Cargo mounts make it easier to load up for long rides</li>\n<li>700 x 45 mm or 650 x 47 mm tire clearance</li>\n<li>Longer, more sure-footed wheelbase</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Warbird_Geometry_2025_dwg.png?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Warbird_Geometry_2025_dwg.png?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Warbird_Geometry_2025_dwg.png?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Warbird_Geometry_2025_dwg.png?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Warbird_Geometry_2025.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Warbird_Geometry_2025.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Warbird_Geometry_2025.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Warbird_Geometry_2025.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Geometry</h3>\n<p>Intended for long days on dirt roads, be it racing or riding, the Warbird’s geometry reflects this riding with longer a wheelbase than its <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/long-term-review-with-the-salsa-warroad-650b-all-road/\" target=\"_blank\">more pavement-friendly Warroad model</a>, a 70.75º head angle, 70 mm of BB drop, and a variable seat angle across the size runs.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_03.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_03.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_03.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_03.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Warbird C GRX 610 1×12 <strong>$2,999</strong></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_01.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_01.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_01.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_01.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Warbird C GRX 820 2×12 <strong>$3,999</strong></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_08.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_08.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_08.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_08.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Warbird C Rival GX AXS 1×12 <strong>$5,299</strong></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_02.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Salsa_Warbird_2025_02.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Warbird C Force AXS Wide 2×12 <strong>$6,999</strong></p>\n<h3>Build Kits</h3>\n<p>2025 Warbirds are now offered in build kits ranging from $2,999 through $6,999 in Shimano and SRAM systems with electronic and cable-actuated shifting.</p>\n<p>Check out more at <a href=\"https://www.salsacycles.com/bikes/road/Warbird\" target=\"_blank\">Salsa Cycles</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/salsa-cycles-warbird-2025-kits-and-colors/\">Salsa Cycles Warbird Gets New Kits and Colors</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"ffe1655a1079df95ac1a02e2c044c3ce4189875ed925facdb68783777b43fe40","category":"Cycling"}